title: Turkmenistan Gross Fixed Capital Formation
description: Gross Fixed Capital Formation in Turkmenistan decreased to 17.23 USD Billion in 2020 from 22.11 USD Billion in 2019. Gross Fixed Capital Formation in Turkmenistan averaged 8.70 USD Billion from 1990 until 2020, reaching an all time high of 22.11 USD Billion in 2019 and a record low of 2.72 USD Billion in 2004. This page provides - Turkmenistan Gross Fixed Capital Formation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: SESRIC - The Statistical, Economic & Social Res. & Training Centre for Islamic Countries
